description:
Take a look at Laodicea from the sky In this Cinematic Aerial Film. Laodicea is located on the river Lycus near to the resort town of Pamukkale, in a lush, green valley in Turkey. When filming for the Lineage 'The 7 Churches of Revelation' series, we captured some incredible views from the skies of Turkey.

 Main Episode: https://youtu.be/5ehXm0pZzIU
 Behind the Scenes: https://youtu.be/6NHWaXCOop4

Laodicea - the last of the seven Churches of Revelation receives no commendation and has the fascinating analogy of lukewarm water used to describe it. What is lukewarmness and why it is too dangerous for our spiritual lives? This message will challenge you to take a discerning look at yourself.
